litative,? Adjustment degrees.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a title="Get Products" href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/get-products/">Buy THE SALESMIND products now »</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'THE SALESMIND - SMARTER SELLING, POWERFUL LIVING', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'the-salesmind-smarter-selling-powerful-living', '', '', '2015-07-14 12:25:53', '2015-07-14 17:25:53', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.dougtrenary.com/?page_id=131', 0, 'page', '', 0),
