(154, 1, '2014-01-06 16:29:16', '2014-01-06 21:29:16', '<h2 id="top_title">GET THE PRODUCTS NOW!</h2>\n"In over twenty years of writing sales training books and certified courses, I''ve never heard a program like the SalesMind. It shoots straight to the realities of selling in today''s world, and makes all the other sales material work better. Any level of student in the sales business can use it. I recommend it to all my clients. Thanks, Doug!"\n\n<em>- Joe Kennedy, Certified Training Instructor</em>\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SALESMIND Book $16.95</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/book.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-242" alt="book" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/book-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" data-id="242" /></a>If you read one personal development book this year, make it "The SalesMind." This fresh look at the new positioning game of sales will knock your socks off with inspiring, practical, and proven strategies of today''s real selling masters. Doug Trenary, a high-powered corporate trainer since 1985, devoted eight years to capturing a 12-point profile of power that will take you way beyond outdated sales strategies to the new world of leveraging yourself, buyers, and time.\n\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/SalesMind-Chapter-One-Sample.pdf">Sample chapter one of this book</a>\n\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND Book" price="16.95"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SUCCESSMIND Book  $11.95</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/book_cover_success_mind.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-278" alt="book_cover_success