ile of power that will take you way beyond outdated sales strategies to the new world of leveraging yourself, buyers, and time.\r\n\r\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND Book" price="16.95"]\r\n<h2>THE SALESMIND 6 CD Audio Set $79.00</h2>\r\nThis powerful reflection of Doug''s book is for the both the beginner and veteran sale pro alike. However, unlike most audio programs, this is not a re-read of the book, but rather a complimentary tool with lots of extra examples, situations, and stories. Hundreds of studio hours were invested to produce a fast-paced, tight audio version of "The SalesMind" for individual or group learning. Doug makes this program special by talking directly to you, the listener, not an auditorium crowd. Fans of the audio program say this conversational aspect is worth the investment alone. The program also comes with a 23-page work guide.\r\n\r\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND 6 CD Audio Set" price="79.00"]\r\n<h2>The Bottom Line 6-CD Set $49.00</h2>\r\nWill you succeed without the rock-solid foundation of proven sales fundamentals? No way. But now, Doug will take you step-by-step through his proven system for sales success in selling anything. The sales closers who gets what they want-including a huge income-know they have to revisit "boot camp" every year to keep their core skills sharp. Doug''s camp will take you deep inside the strategies, techniques, and psychology of every aspect of selling.\r\n\r\n[wp_cart_button name="The Bottom Line 6-CD Set" price="49.00"]\r\n<h2>THE SUCCESSMIND Book  $11.95</h2>\r\nAre you really winning the success game? You will if you''re a SuccessMind! Doug Trenary''s latest riveting work details a totally different approach to winning in life-one that is easy to understand and that anyone can apply. He explains in his unique style how highly successful people master two habits-mental Offense and Defense. Whatever success game you play, The SuccessMind is your game plan to win!\r\n\r\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SUCCESSMIND Book" price="11.95"]\r\n<h2>4 Product Discount  $199.00</h2>\r\nSalesMind book, SalesMind 6 CD''s, Value Game and Unplugged All Four Regular Price $243.95 Discount Package Price $199.00 You Save $44.95 You Save 18%!\r\n\r\n[wp_cart_button name="4 Product Discount" price="199.00"]\r\n<h2>(BEST DEAL) 7 Product Discount  $249.00</h2>\r\nAll Six Regular Price of $341.95. Discount Package Price $249.00. You Save 27%! You will get: The SalesMind Value Game, The SalesMind Unplugged 3-DVD Set, The SalesMind Book, The SalesMind 6 CD Audio Set, The Bottom Line 6-CD Set, Ten Power Closes DVD. Plus you will receive Doug''s new book, "THE SUCCESSMIND" absolutely free!\r\n\r\n[wp_cart_button name="7 Product Discount" price="249.00"]', 'Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 10:35:27', '2013-12-05 10:35:27', '', 11, 'http://www.dev.dougtrenary.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
