(494, 3, '2014-03-07 03:01:54', '2014-03-07 08:01:54', '<h2 id="top_title">GET THE PRODUCTS NOW!</h2>\n"In over twenty years of writing sales training books and certified courses, I''ve never heard a program like the SalesMind. It shoots straight to the realities of selling in today''s world, and makes all the other sales material work better. Any level of student in the sales business can use it. I recommend it to all my clients. Thanks, Doug!"\n\n<em>- Joe Kennedy, Certified Training Instructor</em>\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SALESMIND Book $16.95</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/book.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-242" alt="book" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/book-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" data-id="242" /></a>If you read one personal development book this year, make it "The SalesMind." This fresh look at the new positioning game of sales will knock your socks off with inspiring, practical, and proven strategies of today''s real selling masters. Doug Trenary, a high-powered corporate trainer since 1985, devoted eight years to capturing a 12-point profile of power that will take you way beyond outdated sales strategies to the new world of leveraging yourself, buyers, and time.\n\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/SalesMind-Chapter-One-Sample.pdf">Sample chapter one of this book</a>\n\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND Book" price="16.95"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SUCCESSMIND Book  $11.95</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/book_cover_success_mind.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-278" alt="book_cover_success_mind" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/book_cover_success_mind-192x300.jpg" width="192" height="300" data-id="278" /></a>Are you really winning the success game? You will if you''re a SuccessMind! Doug Trenary''s latest riveting work details a totally different approach to winning in life-one that is easy to understand and that anyone can apply. He explains in his unique style how highly successful people master two habits-mental Offense and Defense. Whatever success game you play, The SuccessMind is your game plan to win!\n\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Sample-Chapter-one-THE-SUCCESSMIND.pdf">Sample chapter one of this book</a>\n\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SUCCESSMIND Book" price="11.95"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SALESMIND 6 CD Audio Set $79.00</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/salesmind-audios.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-276" alt="salesmind audios" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/salesmind-audios-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" data-id="276" /></a>His powerful reflection of Doug''s book is for the both the beginner and veteran sales pro alike. However, unlike most audio programs, this is not a re-read of the book, but rather a complimentary tool with lots of extra examples, situations, and stories. Hundreds of studio hours were invested to produce a fast-paced, tight audio version of "The SalesMind" for individual or group learning. Doug makes this program special by talking directly to you, the listener, not an auditorium crowd. Fans of the audio program say this conversational aspect is worth the investment alone. The program also comes with a 23-page work guide.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[audio mp3="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Leverage_Sample.mp3"][/audio]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND 6 CD Audio Set" price="79.00"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SALESMIND Value Game DVD  $49.00</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/value-game.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-232" alt="value game" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/value-game-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" data-id="232" /></a>It''s a fact--the most successful sales people in the world communicate and deliver value to buyers in every way possible. Value thinking and language consume SalesMinds-and it pays off in income! The SalesMind Value Game will teach you to not only determine what exact value your buyer wants but also to unlock the secrets to integrate value into every sales call-and get the price and profits you want!\n\n&nbsp;\n<div style="width: 300px; float: right; position: relative; top: -40px;">http://www.actionvid.com/dtinteractive/videos/TenValueRulesDemo_small.mp4</div>\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND Value Game DVD" price="49.00" shipping="4.99"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>THE SALESMIND Unplugged 3-DVD  $99.00</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/unplugged.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-235" alt="unplugged" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/unplugged-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" data-id="235" /></a>Can you imagine the leap your business career and income would take if you had a world-class trainer right in your living room teaching you the bottom-line secrets of sales success? Now you can with Doug Trenary''s newest powerhouse DVD set, The SalesMind Unplugged. Discover the most intimate strategies of sales legends in how to increase your own motivation, attract buyers who want to transact now, and turn every minute into a financial opportunity.\n\n&nbsp;\n<div style="width: 300px; float: right; position: relative; top: -40px;">http://www.actionvid.com/dtinteractive/videos/Leverage_Sample_small_1.mp4</div>\n[wp_cart_button name="THE SALESMIND Unplugged 3-DVD" price="99.00"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>The Bottom Line 6-CD Set $49.00</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/bottom-line.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-271" alt="bottom line" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/bottom-line-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" data-id="271" /></a>Will you succeed without the rock-solid foundation of proven sales fundamentals? No way. But now, Doug will take you step-by-step through his proven system for sales success in selling anything. The sales closers who gets what they want-including a huge income-know they have to revisit "boot camp" every year to keep their core skills sharp. Doug''s camp will take you deep inside the strategies, techniques, and psychology of every aspect of selling.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[audio mp3="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/bottom_line_audio.mp3"][/audio]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[wp_cart_button name="The Bottom Line 6-CD Set" price="49.00"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>4 Product Discount  $199.00</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/sales-mind-4x.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-248" alt="sales mind 4x" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/sales-mind-4x-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" data-id="248" /></a>SalesMind book, SalesMind 6 CD''s, Value Game and Unplugged All Four Regular Price $243.95 Discount Package Price $199.00 You Save $44.95 You Save 18%!\n\n[wp_cart_button name="4 Product Discount" price="199.00"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />\n<h3>(BEST DEAL) 6 Product Discount  $249.00</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Bonus-6-set-w-successmind.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-291" alt="Bonus-6-set-w-successmind" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Bonus-6-set-w-successmind-300x201.jpg" width="300" height="201" data-id="291" /></a>All Six Regular Price of $341.95. Discount Package Price $249.00. You Save 27%! You will get: The SalesMind Value Game, The SalesMind Unplugged 3-DVD Set, The SalesMind Book, The SalesMind 6 CD Audio Set, The Bottom Line 6-CD Set, and  "THE SUCCESSMIND" absolutely free!\n\n[wp_cart_button name="7 Product Discount" price="249.00"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img alt="big_shadow" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/big_shadow.png" width="922" height="43" data-id="199" />', 'Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '11-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 03:01:54', '2014-03-07 08:01:54', '', 11, 'http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/11-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
