(535, 3, '2014-03-12 14:48:21', '2014-03-12 19:48:21', '<h6><a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/digital-demo/">Click here to play samples of Doug''s complete<br />Digital SalesMind Program.</a></h6>\r\n\r\n<address style="font-size:14px; font-weight: bold;">To Purchase multiple subscriptions for your company, please select the “Multiple Memberships” product below.</address>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nWhen you buy Doug Trenary University first digital release, “The SalesMind,” you get this complete multi-media package:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>— The SalesMind e-book in its entirety for your Reader</li>\r\n	<li>—The SalesMind  in 23 overview video segments from the “SalesMind Unplugged” sessions recorded in a rare small studio setting</li>\r\n	<li>—The SalesMind complete 6-hour audio program in MP3 files</li>\r\n	<li>—Power Point slides for teaching use in coaching or sales meetings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis multi-media power-house will play on all platforms and on all Ipads, Iphones, tablets, laptops, droid phones, Kindles, Nooks and other e-Readers.\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000; display: none">***NOTE: Please have first name, last name and email address ready at checkout for all users included in the multiple license transaction.  Simply click the Add To Cart button and then choose the number of licenses you wish to purchase when you are at checkout. If you have any questions, please email info@dougtrenary.com***</span>', 'THE DIGITAL SALESMIND', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-digital-salesmind', '', '', '2014-11-11 08:16:07', '2014-11-11 13:16:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=535', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(536, 3, '2014-03-12 14:50:24', '2014-03-12 19:50:24', 'His powerful reflection of Doug''s book is for the both the beginner and veteran sales pro alike. However, unlike most audio programs, this is not a re-read of the book, but rather a complimentary tool with lots of extra examples, situations, and stories. Hundreds of studio hours were invested to produce a fast-paced, tight audio version of "The SalesMind" for individual or group learning. Doug makes this program special by talking directly to you, the listener, not an auditorium crowd. Fans of the audio program say this conversational aspect is worth the investment alone. The program also comes with a 23-page work guide.\r\n\r\n<strong>Play a sample:</strong>\r\n\r\n[audio mp3="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Leverage_Sample.mp3"][/audio]', 'THE SALESMIND 6 CD Audio Set', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-salesmind-6-cd-audio-set', '', '', '2014-11-10 13:18:59', '2014-11-10 18:18:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=536', 4, 'product', '', 0),
