(542, 3, '2014-03-12 16:02:18', '2014-03-12 21:02:18', '<h1>Welcome to your membership area!</h1>\r\n<div id="future-dtu-text">\r\n<div>We are in process of developing a yearly Premium Subscription to Doug Trenary University (DTU). Additionally, this service will offer: • “Director’s Cuts” commentary by Doug via audio on his latest angles on being a SalesMind in today’s world. • A new bi-monthly multi-media newsletter (print, audio, and video) from Doug Trenary devoted to his insights on selling, personal development, peak performance and leadership. • New webinars and commentaries on all these topics. • New live segments of Doug’s speeches and seminars. • Discounts on upcoming new products. So stay tuned, you will receive an email notice when this Premium Subscription is available!</div>\r\n</div>\r\nDoug Trenary, a high-powered corporate trainer since 1985, devoted eight years to capturing a 12-point profile of power that will take you way beyond outdated sales strategies to the new world of leveraging yourself, buyers, and time.\r\n<h3>Your DIGITAL SALESMIND video content is here:</h3>\r\n<address>Click the titles below to view the videos in each section.</address>\r\n<ul class="member_videos">\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Introduction" href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/membership/the-salesmind-introduction/">Introduction</a>  (4 videos)</li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Part 1" href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/membership/the-salesmind-part-1/">Part 1</a> (6 videos)</li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Part 2" href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/membership/the-salesmind-part-2/">Part 2</a> (5 videos)</li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Part 3" href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/membership/the-salesmind-part-3/">Part 3</a> (6 videos)</li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Epilogue &amp; Summary" href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/membership/the-salesmind-epilogue-summary/">Epilogue &amp; Summary </a> (2 videos)</li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind