li><a href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Point_12_Adjustment.mp3">Adjustment: Maximizing Performance</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class="clear">Your DIGITAL SALESMIND eReader content is here:</h3>\r\n<address>On most mobile devices and tablets, the PDF format will be the most compatible. If you use an eReader, you may find the MOBI version more desirable. Follow the instructions from your eReader to import the book onto your device.</address>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/The-Sales-Mind.pdf">The Sales Mind (pdf)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.dougtrenary.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/The Sales Mind - Doug Trenary.mobi">The Sales Mind (mobi)</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Membership', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'membership', '', '', '2015-08-05 06:33:53', '2015-08-05 11:33:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/?page_id=542', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(543, 3, '2014-03-12 16:02:18', '2014-03-12 21:02:18', '<h1>Welcome to your membership area!</h1>\r\n<div id="future-dtu-text">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nWe are in process of developing a yearly Premium Subscription to Doug Trenary University (DTU). Additionally, this service will offer:\r\n\r\n• “Director’s Cuts” commentary by Doug via audio on his latest angles on being a SalesMind in today’s world.\r\n• A new bi-monthly multi-media newsletter (print, audio, and video) from Doug Trenary devoted to his insights on selling, personal development, peak performance and leadership.\r\n• New webinars and commentaries on all these topics.\r\n• New live segments of Doug’s speeches and seminars.\r\n• Discounts on upcoming new products.\r\n\r\nSo stay tuned, you will receive an email notice when this Premium Subscription is available!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nDoug Trenary, a high-powered corporate trainer since 1985, devoted eight years to capturing a 12-point profile of power that will take you way beyond outdated sales strategies to the new world of leveraging yourself, buyers, and time.\r\n<h3>Your DIGITAL SALESMIND video content is here:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Introduction" href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/doug/membership/the-salesmind-introduction/">Introduction</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Part 1" href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/doug/membership/the-salesmind-part-1/">Part 1</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Part 2" href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/doug/membership/the-salesmind-part-2/">Part 2</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Part 3" href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/doug/membership/the-salesmind-part-3/">Part 3</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="The SalesMind Epilogue &amp; Summary" href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/doug/membership/the-salesmind-epilogue-summary/">Epilogue &amp; Summary</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Membership', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '542-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-12 16:02:18', '2