(603, 1, '2014-03-13 13:43:15', '2014-03-13 18:43:15', '<h1 style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/topbar_large.jpg"><img class="size-large wp-image-446" alt="topbar_large" src="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/topbar_large-1024x184.jpg" width="604" height="108" data-id="446" /></a>Law 8 - Leverage</h1>\r\n<table border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;" align="center" width="221"><strong><a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Leverage_Excerpt.doc" target="_blank">Read The Book Excerpts</a></strong></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;" align="center" width="258"><strong><a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Leverage_Sample.mp3" target="_blank">Listen To Accompanying Audio</a></strong></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;" align="center" width="145"><strong><a href="http://localhost/dougtrenary.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/TheSalesMind_Sample.ppt" target="_blank">Teach With Slides</a></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="3">[youtube=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=colPM-BQmKw]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="3" align="center" bgcolor="#FFC52D">\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><strong><em>You Will Get Answers To These Crucial Sales Questions...</em></strong></strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>1) What is Leverage?</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>2) What are the three elements that comprise Leverage?</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>3) What is Cumulative Leverage?</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>4) How do Leverage and Price correspond?</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: cente